                                             rdfs:comment """This file contains ClimOO Ontology imports from the Information Artifact Ontology (IAO). Imports were manually collected and revised as we experienced issues in fletching imports from IAO via OntoFox (https://ontofox.hegroup.org/index.php).

Ontology source: IAO 2022-11-07
https://github.com/information-artifact-ontology/IAO/releases/tag/v2022-11-07

Additional imports from CCO can be found here.
https://github.com/ClimOO/ClimOO-Ontology/tree/main/ClimOO%20material/src/ontology/imports/sumso-imports.ttl"""@en ;
                                             rdfs:seeAlso "https://github.com/information-artifact-ontology/IAO" ;
                                             owl:versionInfo "2025-06-18" .

